verbose_text: At E4.5, a clear separation of cells into the epiblast and PrE is observed and characterized by exclusive expression of known markers, such as Nanog, Esrrb, Fgf4 (epiblast) and Gata6, Pdgfra, and Sox17 (PrE) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY D).
